    "Moreover, our findings demonstrated that perceived ease of use was effectively positive.",
    "This can be because of perceived ease of use and potential opportunities associated with ease of use (or little effort to use) when humans interact with AI or robots (Al-Khateeb et al., 2023; Lim et al., 2023), and so, H3 was accepted.",
